@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Hakkında";
}

<div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#111827] animate-fade-in">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="relative isolate px-6 pt-14 lg:px-8">
        <div class="absolute inset-x-0 -top-40 -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden blur-3xl sm:-top-80" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="relative left-[calc(50%-11rem)] aspect-[1155/678] w-[36.125rem] -translate-x-1/2 rotate-[30deg] bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#8085ff] to-[#543ab7] opacity-30 sm:left-[calc(50%-30rem)] sm:w-[72.1875rem]" style="clip-path: polygon(74.1% 44.1%, 100% 61.6%, 97.5% 26.9%, 85.5% 0.1%, 80.7% 2%, 72.5% 32.5%, 60.2% 62.4%, 52.4% 68.1%, 47.5% 58.3%, 45.2% 34.5%, 27.5% 76.7%, 0.1% 64.9%, 17.9% 100%, 27.6% 76.8%, 76.1% 97.7%, 74.1% 44.1%)"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl py-20 sm:py-28">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-6xl">Finansal Geleceğinizi Şekillendirin</h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Monexia, kişisel finans yönetimini basitleştiren, akıllı içgörüler sunan ve finansal hedeflerinize ulaşmanız için size güç veren modern bir platformdur. Sadece bir harcama izleyiciden daha fazlasıyız; biz sizin kişisel finans asistanınızız.</p>
                <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
                    <a href="/Identity/Account/Register" class="rounded-md bg-indigo-600 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600">Hemen Başlayın</a>
                    <a href="#features" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200">Özellikleri Keşfet <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <div id="features" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">HER ŞEY KONTROL ALTINDA</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">Finansal Yönetimin Geleceği</p>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                Monexia, bütçelemeden yatırım takibine, yapay zeka destekli tavsiyelerden detaylı raporlamaya kadar ihtiyacınız olan her aracı tek bir yerde sunar.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
            <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                        <svg class="h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 6h9.75M10.5 6a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 10-3 0M3.75 6H7.5m3 12h9.75m-9.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-3.75 0H7.5m9-6h3.75m-3.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-9.75 0h9.75" /></svg>
                        Akıllı Bütçeleme ve Limitler
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        <p class="flex-auto">Harcama kategorilerinize özel limitler belirleyin. Monexia sizi limit aşımlarına karşı proaktif olarak uyarır ve bütçenizi korumanıza yardımcı olur.</p>
                    </dd>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                        <svg class="h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18L9 11.25l4.306 4.307a11.95 11.95 0 015.814-5.519l2.74-1.22m0 0l-3.75-.625m3.75.625V3.375" /></svg>
                        Geniş Portföy Yönetimi
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        <p class="flex-auto">Sadece banka hesaplarınızı değil; döviz, kripto para, altın, gümüş ve hisse senedi gibi tüm varlıklarınızı tek bir ekrandan takip edin.</p>
                    </dd>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                        <svg class="h-5 w-5 flex-none text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 14.25v2.25m3-4.5v4.5m3-6.75v6.75m3-9v9M6 20.25h12A2.25 2.25 0 0020.25 18V6A2.25 2.25 0 0018 3.75H6A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 6v12A2.25 2.25 0 006 20.25z" /></svg>
                        Görsel Raporlama
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        <p class="flex-auto">Gelir-gider dağılımı, aylık harcama trendleri ve kategori analizleri gibi onlarca interaktif grafikle finansal durumunuzu anında anlayın.</p>
                    </dd>
                </div>
            </dl>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI Features Section -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900/50 py-20 sm:py-28">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl sm:text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">Yapay Zeka Destekli Finans Koçunuz</h2>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Monexia, OpenAI'ın gücünü kullanarak size özel finansal tavsiyeler sunar ve karmaşık işlemleri basitleştirir.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden pt-16">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
                <img src="~/img/monexia-homepage-icon.png" alt="AI Features" class="mb-[-12%] rounded-xl shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-gray-900/10 mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-20 md:mt-24 lg:px-8">
            <dl class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-10 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-16">
                <div class="relative pl-9">
                    <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                        <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                        Kişiselleştirilmiş Tavsiyeler.
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="inline"> "Ask Monexia" özelliği ile finansal verilerinize dayalı kişiselleştirilmiş sorular sorun ve anında uzman tavsiyeleri alın.</dd>
                </div>
                <div class="relative pl-9">
                    <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                        <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.862 4.487l1.687-1.688a1.875 1.875 0 112.652 2.652L10.582 16.07a4.5 4.5 0 01-1.897 1.13L6 18l.8-2.685a4.5 4.5 0 011.13-1.897l8.932-8.931zm0 0L19.5 7.125M18 14v4.75A2.25 2.25 0 0115.75 21H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 18.75V8.25A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 6H10" /></svg>
                        Otomatik Veri Girişi.
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="inline"> İşlem açıklaması yazdığınızda, yapay zeka en uygun kategoriyi otomatik olarak bularak size zaman kazandırır.</dd>
                </div>
                <div class="relative pl-9">
                    <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                        <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" /></svg>
                        Proaktif Analiz.
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="inline"> Aylık raporlarınız için yönetici özetleri oluşturur ve harcama alışkanlıklarınıza göre akıllı bütçe limitleri önerir.</dd>
                </div>
            </dl>
        </div>
    </div>
</div> 